headline: Airbus Cuts Its Delivery Outlook. Why the Stock Is Up.

content.title: Airbus Cuts Its Delivery Outlook. Why the Stock Is Up.
content.summary: FEATURE  Building airplanes hasn’t been easy lately.  On Wednesday, Boeing peer Airbus cut its full-year delivery forecast by 30 planes. It now expects to deliver about 790 jets in 2025, down from prior guidance, given in October, for 820 jets.
